{"tid":476968,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★資訊科技界明年料加薪最高30％","createTime":"2017-11-22T13:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T10:22:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"2f18872387ca8ca021d13558e7f03ed225e84d76","tid":476968,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:31:32.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】合約聘用模式將成為本港職場的新趨勢！有國際招聘顧問公司昨發表薪酬調查報告，分析和展望明年的招聘市場情況，認為本港採用合約聘用形式成為新趨勢，僱主希望尋找具特定經驗的人才負責專案項目，當中最常見為金融服務及人力資源行業；加上年輕一代追求生活和工作平衡，更多人傾向以合約形式工作，僱主亦願意為合約員工提供更好的福利和薪酬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時各行各業對科技界人才皆求才若渴，因此熟悉大數據、網絡安全和雲端技術的科技人才最受市場青睞，預計這些人才來年薪酬加幅可高達三成，而資訊科技行業的平均加薪幅度亦達一成至一成半，轉職的合約員工薪酬增幅也有一成半至兩成。因此，資訊科技界成為來年薪酬加幅最多的行業，人力資源行業的加幅則最少，平均只有百分之二至百分之三。<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171122/00176_074.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171122%2F00176_074.html&d=Lrz33MO9%2FF%2BgA77gwrfowVeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=7fea8f33\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171122/00176_074.html</a>"},{"pid":"602e0d8cb4510d7896fabc8c5fd8a724e80f861e","tid":476968,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:32:40.000Z","msg":"IT有前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62af7d06ab1c7c5a40ed48542a9de0224bdf7e99","tid":476968,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:37:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 吹夠未..."},{"pid":"240285b0d88cd333210e1f41de1de047b5b6a9d6","tid":476968,"uid":52062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:40:16.000Z","msg":"最高...<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又出口術<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0566d0eac72aec09e6920c24399e02d794d1f1a1","tid":476968,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"cit